<td align="center"><b>
<i>Nomada texana</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cresson, 1872</font></b><br>
<small><i>Nomada heiligbrodtii </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Cephen texanus </i>&#40;Cresson, 1872&#41;; <i>Hypochrotaenia &#40;Micronomada&#41; heiligbrodtii </i>&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;; <i>Hypochrotaenia &#40;Micronomada&#41; texana </i>&#40;Cresson, 1878&#41;</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
